    <!-- /.content-tab-panel -->
    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: This guideline updates a previous version: Australian guidelines for the treatment of adults with acute stress disorder and posttraumatic stress disorder. Melbourne (Australia): Australian Centre for Posttraumatic Mental Health; 2007 Feb.</p>
<p>In recognition of the pace of advances in the field, it is recommended that the guidelines be reviewed and updated in five years' time.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
