                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0004933&amp;fLockTerm=Behavior+therapy">Behavior therapy</a>
 (94.33), <a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0015618&amp;fLockTerm=Family+therapy">Family therapy</a>
 (94.42), <a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0038436&amp;fLockTerm=Posttraumatic+stress+disorder">Posttraumatic stress disorder</a>
 (309.81), <a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0236816&amp;fLockTerm=Unspecified+acute+reaction+to+stress">Unspecified acute reaction to stress</a>
 (308.9)                    </div>
