    <li>A number of fact sheets and booklets for people affected by trauma, their families and friends are available from the <a href="/web/20180712204944/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49219&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fphoenixaustralia.org%2frecovery%2ffact-sheets-and-booklets%2f" title="Phoenix Australia - Centre for Posttraumatic Mental Health Web site">Phoenix Australia - Centre for Posttraumatic Mental Health Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712204944im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
